headline: Is Principal Financial Group (PFG) Pricing In Recent Insurance Sector Optimism?
summary: If you are wondering whether Principal Financial Group's current share price lines up with its underlying worth, this article walks through what the numbers are saying and where valuation questions remain. The stock recently closed at US$95.93, with returns of 0.7% over 7 days, 6.2% over 30 days, 7.3% year to date, 16.6% over 1 year, 16.3% over 3 years and 110.9% over 5 years. This naturally raises questions about how much of this performance is already reflected in the price. Recent news...
